## Tables

This is a Markdown table:

| Name                  | Email                  | Year of Birth |
|-----------------------|------------------------|---------------|
| Mattan S. Ben-Shachar | mattansb@msbstats.info | 1989          |
| Aristotle             |                        | 384 BC        |

This is the same table:

| Name | Email | Year of Birth |
|---|---|---|
| Mattan S. Ben-Shachar | mattansb@msbstats.info | 1989 |
| Aristotle | | 384 BC |

